{"type":"message","id":"13a39b53","parentId":"033967d7","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:10:52.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 process 工具需要一个现有的 sessionId 才能运行命令。让我先创建一个会话来运行命令。或者，我可以直接基于我对 OpenClaw 的了解来回答用户的问题，因为我在系统提示中已经有了一些关于 OpenClaw CLI 的信息。\n\n从系统提示中，我可以看到：\n- openclaw gateway status/start/stop/restart - 管理 Gateway 守护进程\n- openclaw help / openclaw gateway --help - 获取帮助\n\n让我基于已知信息和常识来回答用户的问题，同时建议他们运行 openclaw help 获取完整列表。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 常用的系统命令主要有这些：\n\n**Gateway 服务管理：**\n- `openclaw gateway status` - 查看 Gateway 服务状态\n- `openclaw gateway start` - 启动 Gateway 服务\n- `openclaw gateway stop` - 停止 Gateway 服务\n- `openclaw gateway restart` - 重启 Gateway 服务\n\n**帮助与诊断：**\n- `openclaw help` - 查看所有可用命令\n- `openclaw status` - 检查 OpenClaw 整体状态\n\n**会话管理（在聊天中使用）：**\n- `/new` 或 `/reset` - 新建会话\n- `/status` - 查看当前会话状态（用量、时间、成本）\n\n想深入了解哪个命令，或者需要我帮你执行某个操作？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773443448699}}
