{"type":"message","id":"ccafdb02","parentId":"f78c9dbc","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:29:26.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置已修改完成。现在需要向用户汇报已完成的修改，并说明如何使用分层模型策略。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置已更新。分层策略如下：\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已完成配置\n\n### 模型层级\n| 层级 | 模型 | 使用方式 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| **light** | qwen-turbo | 心跳、后台任务 |\n| **standard** | qwen3.5-plus | 默认日常 |\n| **max** | qwen3-max-2026-01-23 | 复杂任务 |\n| **kimi** | kimi-k2.5 | 备选旗舰 |\n| **vl** | qwen-vl-plus | 视觉任务 |\n| **tts** | qwen3-tts-flash | 语音输出 |\n| **draw** | qwen-image-2.0 | 图像生成 |\n\n### 使用方式\n\n**手动切换（聊天中）：**\n- `/model light` → 快速响应\n- `/model max` → 最强推理\n- `/model vl` → 看图\n- `/model tts` → 语音\n\n**自动 fallback：**\n- 主模型失败时自动切 `kimi-k2.5` → `qwen-plus`\n\n---\n\n## 下一步建议\n\n1. **重启 Gateway** 使配置生效：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n\n2. **测试分层**：\n   - 日常对话用默认（standard）\n   - 复杂任务用 `/model max`\n\n3. **可选：配置自动路由**（高级）\n   - 根据任务类型自动选模型\n   - 需要我帮你配吗？\n\n配置已保存，需要现在重启 Gateway 吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773444560879}}
