{"type":"message","id":"85a950d0","parentId":"61f79619","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:30:48.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已读取完整配置，现在整理并展示当前的模型分层策略配置状态给用户确认。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前配置已更新，分层模型策略如下：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前模型配置\n\n### 默认模型（agents.defaults）\n```json\n{\n  \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n  \"fallbacks\": [\n    \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"dashscope/qwen-plus\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### CEO Agent 专属配置（agents.list[0]）\n```json\n{\n  \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n  \"fallbacks\": [\n    \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n    \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\"\n  ],\n  \"modelLayers\": {\n    \"light\": \"dashscope/qwen-turbo\",       // 轻量级\n    \"standard\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",  // 默认\n    \"max\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",  // 旗舰\n    \"kimi\": \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\",  // 备选旗舰\n    \"vl\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-plus\",        // 视觉\n    \"tts\": \"dashscope-audio/qwen3-tts-flash\",  // 语音\n    \"draw\": \"dashscope-image/qwen-image-2.0\"   // 绘图\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 使用方式\n\n| 命令 | 切换到 |\n|------|--------|\n| `/model light` | qwen-turbo（最快最便宜） |\n| `/model standard` 或 `/model coding` | qwen3.5-plus（默认） |\n| `/model max` | qwen3-max（最强推理） |\n| `/model kimi` | kimi-k2.5（备选旗舰） |\n| `/model vl` | qwen-vl-plus（看图） |\n| `/model tts` | qwen3-tts-flash（语音） |\n| `/model draw` | qwen-image-2.0（绘图） |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 注意\n\n配置已保存但**尚未生效**，需要重启 Gateway：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者等配置热重载（约 300ms 内自动应用）。\n\n需要我帮你检查 Gateway 状态吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773444639656}}
