{"type":"message","id":"504a3a88","parentId":"32fccc1b","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:32:14.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent failed to restart the Gateway because Docker is not available on this Windows machine. The error shows it tried to connect to Docker Desktop but the daemon isn't running.\n\nI need to inform the user about this issue and suggest alternatives. The Gateway restart might still work through other means, or we can try a different approach.\n\nLet me communicate this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 重启失败了——原因是 **Docker 服务未运行**。\n\n错误信息：无法连接到 Docker Desktop 引擎。\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n### 选项 1：启动 Docker Desktop\n```bash\n# 手动打开 Docker Desktop 应用\n# 或者在 PowerShell 中：\nStart-Process \"Docker Desktop\"\n```\n等 Docker 启动完成后，再执行：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 选项 2：不用 Docker，直接重启 Gateway\n如果你的 Gateway 不是运行在 Docker 容器里，可以直接用 CLI 重启：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway stop\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n或者如果 Gateway 是作为服务安装的：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n---\n\n## ❓ 需要确认\n\n你的 Gateway 是：\n- **A.** 作为 Windows 服务运行（推荐）→ 用选项 2\n- **B.** 在 Docker 容器里运行 → 需要先启动 Docker Desktop\n- **C.** 前台手动运行 → 需要手动停止后重新启动\n\n你用的是哪种方式？我帮你执行对应的重启命令。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773444723252}}
