{"type":"message","id":"29c620b5","parentId":"c882a591","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:38:09.726Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在配置已修复：\n1. 移除了无效的 `modelLayers` 字段\n2. 添加了 `light` 别名对应 `dashscope/qwen-turbo`\n\n现在 Gateway 应该可以正常重启了。让我告诉用户配置已修复，以及如何使用模型切换。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置已修复：\n- ✅ 移除了无效的 `modelLayers` 字段\n- ✅ 添加了 `light` 别名（qwen-turbo）\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前可用模型别名\n\n| 别名 | 模型 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `light` | qwen-turbo | 轻量快速 |\n| `coding` | qwen3.5-plus | 默认日常 |\n| `max` | qwen3-max | 最强推理 |\n| `kimi` | kimi-k2.5 | 备选旗舰 |\n| `plus-paygo` | qwen-plus | 备用 |\n| `vl` | qwen-vl-plus | 视觉 |\n| `tts` | qwen3-tts-flash | 语音 |\n| `draw` | qwen-image-2.0 | 绘图 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 现在可以重启了\n\n在 PowerShell 中执行：\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者在 Control UI 中点击 **Apply & Restart**。\n\n重启后，用 `/model <别名>` 切换模型，例如：\n- `/model light` → 快速响应\n- `/model max` → 复杂任务\n- `/model coding` → 回到默认\n\n需要我帮你执行重启吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773445081089}}
