{"type":"message","id":"a1e297ec","parentId":"9617aa20","timestamp":"2026-03-13T23:40:45.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我刚才改了 openclaw.json 的什么内容，我需要回顾刚才的编辑操作，清晰地列出改动。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我刚才做了两处修改：\n\n---\n\n## 1. 移除了无效字段 `modelLayers`\n\n**问题：** 我添加了一个不存在的配置字段 `modelLayers`，导致配置验证失败。\n\n**修改位置：** `agents.list[0]`（CEO Agent 配置）\n\n**删除内容：**\n```json\n\"modelLayers\": {\n  \"light\": \"dashscope/qwen-turbo\",\n  \"standard\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n  \"max\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\",\n  \"kimi\": \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\",\n  \"vl\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-plus\",\n  \"tts\": \"dashscope-audio/qwen3-tts-flash\",\n  \"draw\": \"dashscope-image/qwen-image-2.0\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 添加了 `light` 模型别名\n\n**修改位置：** `agents.defaults.models`\n\n**新增内容：**\n```json\n\"dashscope/qwen-turbo\": {\n  \"alias\": \"light\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n| 操作 | 原因 |\n|------|------|\n| 删除 `modelLayers` | 这不是 OpenClaw 支持的有效字段 |\n| 添加 `light` 别名 | 让 `qwen-turbo` 可以用 `/model light` 切换 |\n\n---\n\n**正确的分层方式** 是用 `agents.defaults.models` 定义模型别名，然后用 `/model <别名>` 手动切换，而不是用 `modelLayers` 自动路由。\n\n这个教训我已经记下了——改配置前先确认字段是否有效。🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773445234553}}
