{"type":"message","id":"803b9f56","parentId":"9128e0fd","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:31:56.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！`agents.list[0]`（main/CEO Agent）的配置中**没有独立的 tools 配置**，它依赖的是 `agents.defaults.tools`。\n\n但是配置文件中 `tools` 是在根目录下，不是在 `agents.defaults` 下。这意味着：\n1. 根目录的 `tools` 配置是全局的\n2. 但每个 Agent 可以有自己的 `tools` 配置覆盖\n\n让我检查 `agents.defaults` 是否有 tools 配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9b0bc15909ed425e8b39acf0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":100,"offset":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773487896924}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e374a31","parentId":"803b9f56","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:31:57.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9b0bc15909ed425e8b39acf0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n        \"fallbacks\": [\n          \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\",\n          \"dashscope/qwen-plus\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"imageModel\": {\n        \"primary\": \"dashscope-image/qwen-image-2.0\",\n        \"fallbacks\": []\n      },\n      \"pdfModel\": {\n        \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\",\n        \"fallbacks\": [\n          \"dashscope/qwen-vl-plus\"\n        ]\n      },\n      \"pdfMaxBytesMb\": 10,\n      \"pdfMaxPages\": 20,\n      \"models\": {\n        \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\": {\n          \"alias\": \"coding\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope-coding/kimi-k2.5\": {\n          \"alias\": \"kimi\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\": {\n          \"alias\": \"max\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope/qwen-plus\": {\n          \"alias\": \"plus-paygo\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope/qwen-turbo\": {\n          \"alias\": \"light\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope/qwen-vl-plus\": {\n          \"alias\": \"vl\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope-image/qwen-image-2.0\": {\n          \"alias\": \"draw\"\n        },\n        \"dashscope-audio/qwen3-tts-flash\": {\n          \"alias\": \"tts\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"repoRoot\": \"~/Projects/openclaw\",\n      \"skipBootstrap\": false,\n      \"bootstrapMaxChars\": 20000,\n      \"bootstrapTotalMaxChars\": 300000,\n      \"bootstrapPromptTruncationWarning\": \"always\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"contextPruning\": {\n        \"mode\": \"cache-ttl\",\n        \"ttl\": \"1h\",\n        \"keepLastAssistants\": 3,\n        \"softTrimRatio\": 0.3,\n        