{"type":"message","id":"a38fa764","parentId":"7e374a31","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:32:20.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现问题了！在 `agents.defaults.contextPruning.tools.deny` 中，`browser` 和 `canvas` 被禁止了，但这不影响 `web_search`。\n\n让我继续检查 main Agent 是否有独立的 tools 配置，以及根目录的 tools 配置是否正确应用。\n\n实际上，问题可能是：\n1. 根目录的 `tools` 配置是全局默认配置\n2. 但 main Agent 在 `agents.list` 中没有继承这个配置\n\n让我检查 OpenClaw 的配置结构，看看 tools 配置应该如何正确应用到 Agent 上。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1c809157a565492ca0543499","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":50,"offset":390}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773487917002}}
