{"type":"message","id":"8d62a0bd","parentId":"492a8933","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:33:05.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 重启任务已启动，等待完成通知。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已启动 Gateway 重启，等待完成通知...\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 问题诊断与修复总结\n\n### 问题原因\n**main Agent 没有独立的 `tools` 配置**，只依赖根目录全局配置，导致工具不可用。\n\n### 修复内容\n在 `agents.list[0].main` 中添加了明确的 `tools` 配置：\n```json\n{\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"profile\": \"coding\",\n    \"allow\": [\n      \"browser\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"process\",\n      \"sessions_list\",\n      \"sessions_history\",\n      \"sessions_send\",\n      \"sessions_spawn\",\n      \"session_status\",\n      \"subagents\",\n      \"cron\",\n      \"gateway\",\n      \"image\",\n      \"canvas\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"web_search\",\n      \"web_fetch\",\n      \"message\"\n    ],\n    \"deny\": [...]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 验证方法\nGateway 重启后，尝试：\n```\n搜索：面粉品牌推荐\n```\n\n应该可以正常使用 `web_search` 工具了。\n\n需要我帮你测试吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773487981395}}
