{"type":"message","id":"cf593c0f","parentId":"6fb44a4d","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:33:25.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The first subagent task failed due to Docker not being available (sandbox issue we identified earlier). This is expected since we haven't fixed the Docker/sandbox issue yet.\n\nNow I need to wait for the second subagent (Gateway restart) to complete before I can confirm the fix is applied.\n\nLet me provide a status update to the user about what happened and what's being done.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第一个测试任务因为 Docker 沙箱问题失败了（这是我们之前讨论过的沙箱未启用问题）。\n\nGateway 重启任务已经在进行中，重启完成后 `web_search` 应该就可以正常使用了。\n\n---\n\n## 📊 当前状态\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 配置修复 | ✅ 已完成 |\n| Gateway 重启 | ⏳ 进行中 |\n| web_search 可用性 | ⏸️ 等待重启后验证 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 关于沙箱问题\n\n刚才的测试再次遇到 Docker 沙箱连接失败。这是因为我用 `subagent` 执行命令时默认会尝试使用沙箱。\n\n**临时解决方案：** 我可以直接用非沙箱方式执行命令，或者你在 PowerShell 中手动执行：\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\nGateway 重启完成后，试试输入：\n```\n搜索：面粉品牌推荐\n```\n\n应该就可以正常使用了。需要我现在帮你测试吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773487985469}}
