{"type":"message","id":"6bb5cacd","parentId":"c9666058","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:33:32.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 重启任务也因为 Docker 沙箱问题失败了。我需要告诉用户配置已修复，但需要手动重启 Gateway。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway 重启任务也因为 Docker 沙箱问题失败了。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 配置已修复，需要手动重启\n\n配置修改已完成，但 Gateway 需要重启才能生效。由于沙箱未启用，自动重启失败了。\n\n**请在 PowerShell 中执行：**\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n或者分两步：\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway stop\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 修复内容回顾\n\n在 `openclaw.json` 中给 main Agent 添加了明确的 `tools` 配置，包含 `web_search` 工具。\n\n重启后，你就可以使用：\n```\n搜索：面粉品牌推荐\n```\n\n---\n\n需要我等你重启后再帮你测试吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773488005513}}
