{"type":"message","id":"0e4df9f9","parentId":"c79ba28d","timestamp":"2026-03-14T12:27:07.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"web_fetch 也失败了，可能是因为百度搜索结果页面是动态加载的，Readability 无法提取内容。\n\n让我换一个策略 - 直接给用户基于知识推荐，然后说明网络限制问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"web_fetch 也失败了（百度搜索结果页是动态的，无法提取）。\n\n---\n\n## 🥟 直接给你推荐（基于通用知识）\n\n### 包包子面粉推荐\n\n| 品牌 | 系列 | 特点 | 参考价 |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| **香满园** | 中筋面粉 | 性价比高，包子馒头通用 | ~3 元/斤 |\n| **金龙鱼** | 中筋面粉 | 品质稳定，超市常见 | ~3.5 元/斤 |\n| **五得利** | 五星中筋 | 老牌面粉，筋度好 | ~2.5 元/斤 |\n| **福临门** | 中筋面粉 | 中粮出品，可靠 | ~3 元/斤 |\n| **新良** | 包子饺子粉 | 专用配方，更细腻 | ~4 元/斤 |\n\n### 购买建议\n- **日常家用**：香满园或金龙鱼\n- **追求口感**：新良包子饺子专用粉\n- **批量购买**：五得利 5kg 装\n\n---\n\n## 📋 总结\n\n| 问题 | 原因 | 解决 |\n|------|------|------|\n| web_search 报错 | Brave API 需要国际网络 | 用 browser 工具 或 配置代理 |\n| web_fetch 报错 | 动态页面无法提取 | 直接问我或换静态页面 |\n\n需要我帮你配置其他搜索引擎吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773491222866}}
{"type":"message","id":"590c1d76","parentId":"0e4df9f9","timestamp":"2026-03-14T12:28:04.229Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-14 20:28 GMT+8] 那就使用browser 代替 web_search把"}],"timestamp":1773491284219}}
{"type":"message","id":"db41265f","parentId":"590c1d76","timestamp":"2026-03-14T12:28:10.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户决定用 browser 代替 web_search，我需要确认这个选择并说明如何配置和使用 browser 工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"# ✅ 已确认：使用 browser 代替 web_search\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置检查\n\nbrowser 工具已经在你的配置中启用了：\n\n```json\n\"tools\": {\n  \"allow\": [\n    \"browser\",\n    \"read\",\n    \"write\",\n    ...\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**无需修改配置**，直接使用即可。\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 使用方法\n\n### 方式 1：直接让我用 browser 搜索\n\n```\n用 browser 搜索：面粉品牌推荐\n```\n\n### 方式 2：在对话中指定\n\n```\n帮我搜索一下包子用什么面粉好，用 browser\n```\n\n### 方式 3：自动 fallback（推荐配置）\n\n可以配置当 web_search 失败时自动使用 browser：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"web\": {\n    \"search\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"provider\": \"brave\",\n      \"fallback\": \"browser\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 现在帮你搜索\n\n让我用 browser 帮你搜索面粉品牌推荐：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3f3f89525205438bab79c0db","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"用 browser 工具搜索：面粉品牌推荐 包子馒头用 2025，然后总结推荐","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773491284225}}
