{"type":"message","id":"5a54e3a4","parentId":"0b633f0e","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:02:15.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索还是报错了。可能是 Gateway 没有真正重启，或者 Tavily API 需要代理。让我检查一下配置是否正确加载，并尝试用 process 直接执行重启命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"还是报错。让我直接用 process 执行重启命令：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03e44585793e42b380768009","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"run","command":"openclaw gateway restart","timeoutMs":"10000"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773493304448}}
