{"type":"message","id":"49999a5c","parentId":"19992f98","timestamp":"2026-03-14T13:02:50.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"process 工具需要 sessionId，但我没有。让我试试用 sessions_spawn 但这次用不同的方式，或者直接在当前会话中执行。\n\n其实配置修改后，Gateway 应该会自动检测并重载。让我再试一次搜索，或者检查配置是否真的生效了。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我再试一次搜索，或者 Gateway 需要手动重启：\n\n**请在 PowerShell 中执行：**\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置已更新\n\n```json\n{\n  \"web\": {\n    \"search\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"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\",\n      \"maxResults\": 5,\n      \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 可能的问题\n\n如果重启后还是报错，可能是：\n\n1. **Tavily API 需要代理** — 中国大陆访问可能需要\n2. **API Key 格式问题** — dev key 可能有特殊配置\n3. **Gateway 未重载配置** — 需要手动重启\n\n---\n\n**请先在 PowerShell 执行重启命令，然后告诉我结果，我再帮你测试。** 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773493335456}}
