{"type":"message","id":"fab38fbf","parentId":"1f8208e3","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:45:00.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置看起来正确，但搜索还是失败。可能 Gateway 没有重新加载配置。让我让用户手动重启 Gateway，或者尝试直接用 Tavily 插件的方式搜索。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置已更新为 Tavily，但 Gateway 可能需要手动重启才能加载新配置。\n\n**请在 PowerShell 中执行：**\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n重启完成后，我就可以用 Tavily 搜索了。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置总结\n\n| 配置项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| openclaw-tavily 插件 | ✅ 已安装 (v0.2.1) |\n| Tavily API Key | ✅ 已配置 |\n| web.search.provider | ✅ 已改为 tavily |\n| Gateway 重启 | ⏸️ 需要手动执行 |\n\n---\n\n**请重启 Gateway 后告诉我，我再测试 Tavily 搜索。** 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773499465519}}
