{"type":"message","id":"040e91ce","parentId":"fe23ff03","timestamp":"2026-03-14T14:54:47.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户报告了配置错误，说 tavily 不是有效的 provider 选项。让我检查 OpenClaw 支持的搜索 provider，并改回有效的选项。\n\n根据错误信息，允许的 provider 是：brave, perplexity, grok, gemini, kimi\n\nTavily 不在列表中，说明 OpenClaw 不直接支持 Tavily 作为 web.search.provider。openclaw-tavily 插件可能是通过其他方式集成的，而不是通过 web.search.provider 配置。\n\n让我先改回 brave，然后研究一下 openclaw-tavily 插件的正确用法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！OpenClaw 的 `web.search.provider` 不支持 `tavily`，允许的只有：`brave`, `perplexity`, `grok`, `gemini`, `kimi`。\n\n`openclaw-tavily` 插件可能是通过其他方式集成的，不是通过 `web.search.provider` 配置。\n\n让我先改回 `brave`，然后研究 Tavily 插件的正确用法：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e785602f970d443d98f0791c","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","oldText":"    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"provider\": \"tavily\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"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\",\n        \"maxResults\": 5,\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"fetch\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"maxChars\": 50000,\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30,\n        \"userAgent\": \"OpenClaw/1.0\"\n      }\n    },","newText":"    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"provider\": \"brave\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"BSAAg5L5kNDIJY9C0R4JrJcuKyRjfdo\",\n        \"maxResults\": 5,\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30\n      },\n      \"fetch\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"maxChars\": 50000,\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 30,\n        \"userAgent\": \"OpenClaw/1.0\"\n      }\n    },"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17