{"type":"message","id":"7a1f91fd","parentId":"a6b32781","timestamp":"2026-03-14T15:30:42.995Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`web_search` 还是失败，因为它用的是 Brave 配置。Tavily 插件提供的是独立工具 `tavily_search`，不是替换 `web.search`。\n\n让我尝试用 Tavily 插件的工具来搜索。但是我需要用正确的方式调用它。根据插件文档，工具名是 `tavily_search`，我应该让子代理使用这个工具。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`web_search` 用的是 Brave 配置，不是 Tavily。让我用 Tavily 插件的独立工具测试：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7507dbdd10904d80a6692271","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"使用 tavily_search 工具搜索：2026 年 3 月最新新闻，count=5","timeoutSeconds":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773502233796}}
